Day 92: Managing Jinja2 Templates Using Ansible

Date: December 21, 2025
Overview
Created dynamic configuration files using Jinja2 templates.
Key Concepts Learned

Template module
Jinja2 syntax
Variable substitution
Conditional templates

Template File (config.j2)
jinja2server {
    listen 80;
    server_name {{ domain_name }};
    root {{ document_root }};
    
    {% if ssl_enabled %}
    listen 443 ssl;
    ssl_certificate {{ ssl_cert_path }};
    {% endif %}
}
Playbook
yaml- name: Deploy nginx config from template
  template:
    src: config.j2
    dest: /etc/nginx/conf.d/site.conf
    owner: root
    mode: '0644'
  notify: restart nginx

Challenges Faced
Template syntax errors and variable scope iss
